<li class="commentbody highlighted" id="comment-308614">
			<cite><a href='http://smittenkitchen.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>deb</a></cite>
						&nbsp;
			<a class="commentlink" href="#comment-308614" title="">July 23, 2009</a> 

		
			<div class="commentcount">40</div>

				<p>It will depend on the recipe, but no, all stocks have different effects. To me, the beef stock flavor is central to traditional onion soup. But that doesn&#8217;t mean you can&#8217;t make a delicious one with vegetable or mushroom stocks.</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
<li class="commentbody" id="comment-323634">
