			<div class="commentcount">41</div>

				<p>Sireesha, if you want a &#8216;fuller&#8217; flavour you may want to try adding a bit of something like vegemite or marmite to the stock.  It has an added savoury-ness to it that may mimic beef stock nicely.  You&#8217;ll have to do it to taste however as I&#8217;ve only hear it be recommended before and never tried it outside of a vegemite sandwhich or 9 :)</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
